                 <!-- note on edition: 1. ḥ > h, 2 paten (·) are deleted, 3. ṁ > ṅ, 4. ṁṅ > ṅ -->
	<p><pb n="A1v"/>ndah nihan varahakna saṅ sadu, <app><lem wit="#A">de</lem><rdg wit="#B">den</rdg></app> saṅ mamet hayu, hana ta <app><lem type="conj" wit="E">saṅ h</lem><note>Mss. AB are dammage in this part</note></app>yaṅ ṣikṣa kandaṅ karəṣian ṅaranya, kayatnak<unclear>na</unclear> voṅ sakabeh, ujar saṅ sadu, ṅagəlarkәn saṅ hyaṅ sikṣa kandaṅ karәṣian,</p>
                <p>ini saṅ hyaṅ dasakrәta, kundaṅən uraṅ <app><lem type="norm">rea</lem><rdg wit="#A #B">rye</rdg></app>, <app><lem wit="#A"><unclear>asiṅ nu dek</unclear></lem><rdg type="lacune" wit="#B"/></app> <app><lem type="emend">nañjərkən</lem><rdg wit="#A">najərkən</rdg><rdg wit="#B"><gap reason="lost"></gap></rdg></app> saṅ hyaṅ sasana krəta, pakənən hәbәl hirup həbəl <app><lem type="emend">ñovana</lem><rdg wit="#A #B">ñavana</rdg></app>, <app><lem type="norm">jadian</lem><rdg wit="#A">jadyan</rdg><rdg wit="#B"><gap reason="lost"/></rdg></app> kuras <app><lem type="emend">jadian</lem><rdg wit="#A">jadya</rdg></app> tahun dәgdәg tajәr <app><lem>jaya</lem><rdg wit="#A">ya</rdg><rdg wit="#B"><gap reason="lost"/></rdg></app> praṅ, ñovana na <app><lem wit="#B">uraṅ</lem><rdg wit="#A"><unclear>u</unclear>raṅ</rdg></app> <app><lem type="norm">rea</lem><rdg wit="#A #B">rye</rdg></app>,</p>
                <p><app><lem wit="#B">ini</lem><rdg wit="#A"><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/>ni</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#A">byaktana</lem><rdg wit="#B">byitana</rdg></app> saṅ hyaṅ <app><lem wit="A">dasakrәta</lem><rdg wit="#B">dasakrata</rdg></app> ṅaranya, kalaṅkaṅ saṅ hyaṅ dasa-<app><lem wit="#A">sila</lem><rdg><gap reason="lost"/></rdg><note>From this passage Ms. B is ommited until the word ... in <ref>...</ref><!-- Adit: How to refer the word and number of </p> elements? -->, the reason why I do not indicate ms. B readings.</note></app>, maya-maya saṅ hyaṅ dasamarga, kaprәtyakṣaan na dasa-indriya, pakәn ṅrәtakәn di bumi lamba, di bumi <app><lem type="emend">parәk</lem><rdg wit="#A">paR̥<unclear>ka</unclear></rdg></app>,</p> 
                <p>ini pakәn uraṅ ṅrәtakәn bumi <app><lem type="conj">la<supplied reason="lost" evidence="previouseditor" source="Atja+Danasasmita1981_01">mba caaṅ ja</supplied>lan</lem><rdg wit="#A">la<gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="4"/><unclear>ja</unclear>lan·</rdg></app> pañjaṅ tajur, paka pradana, liñih pipiṙ <app><lem>caaṅ</lem><rdg wit="#A">paA</rdg></app> bu<pb n="A2r"/>ruan,</p>
                
